INDEX OF HELP TOPICS

Due to the large number of help topics available, please try
one of the following subtopics below:

help classes		      to find out what kind of character to be
help movement                 getting around in the world
help communications           how to converse with other players
help spell info               information for spellcasters and their targets
help object manipulation      how to interact with the world around you
help general info             how to get general information about yourself
                              and the world around you
help combat                   topics relating to bloodshed and general carnage
help utility                  changing your interface with the world, etc.
help social                   social commands to 
help god	              listing of the wiz commands having help files.
				(god access only)
	
See also HELP for a list of possible commands.
